item.description:
Photo Critique session planned at L.B. Wheaton. Usually we have some
form of registration on the web site but this time we're just
asking for an email notice. Here's a copy of the facebook
announcement.

LB Wheaton's next workshop is going to be on November 3rd at 6:00 PM.
The topic? A critique of your work, where we will focus on
helping your skills progress where you need it most. Every
participant will have one on one time. $10 reservation fee that
once here, goes towards any purchase.

Email info@lbwheaton.com to register!
